{"tid":693421,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新盤混戰】白石角嘉熙暫收3,700票 超額12倍","createTime":"2018-06-07T12:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T12:36:41.000Z","uid":68476,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0717ea2af190fb8733047638c5fa54bab640c3bd","tid":693421,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"【新盤混戰】白石角嘉熙暫收3,700票 超額12倍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180607/large/1528357071_9958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180607%2Flarge%2F1528357071_9958.jpg&h=1e90e1c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">嘉熙會所將設1至2部3D打印設機，為業主提供3D打印服務</span><br />\n<br />\n新盤市況熾熱，嘉華（173)大埔白石角嘉熙公佈最新銷售消息，集團國際營業及市場策劃總經理（香港地產）溫偉明表示，截至下午3時項目收票約3,700票，以周六銷售的次輪268伙計算，超額約12倍，今日下午5時截票。項目亦公佈最新會所資料，會所將設1至2部3D打印設機，為客戶提供3D打印服務，管理費將參考同區價格。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">3D打印層樓出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"}]}